Class SteamId

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.iwyfewwnt.steamid.SteamId
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable

    public final class SteamId
extends Object
implements Serializable, Cloneable
    A Steam ID representation.

    SteamId is the class that represents Steam ID as an entity and includes a lot of methods to convert and parse to/from any Steam related data.
